Package: CausCor
Title: Calculate Correlations and Estimate Causality
Version: 0.1.3
Authors@R: 
    person("Tomomi", "Sugiyama", email = "sugiyama.t.am@m.titech.ac.jp", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This tool performs pairwise correlation analysis and estimate causality.
    Particularly, it is useful for detecting the metabolites that would be altered by the gut bacteria.
URL: https://github.com/sugym/CausCor
